Homepage: http://www.geocities.com/user42_kevin/html-formatexternal/index.html
Bugs: mailto:user42@zip.com.au

Package: libhtml-formatexternal-perl
Architecture: all
Depends: perl (>= 5.8), libperl6-slurp-perl, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: lynx | elinks | links | netrik | w3m | zen
Suggests: elinks, links, lynx, netrik, w3m, zen
Description: Format HTML to text in perl using external programs
 HTML::FormatExternal turns HTML into plain text by running it through
 one of elinks, links, lynx, netrik, w3m or zen.  The programming
 interface is compatible with HTML::FormatText and other
 HTML::Formatter classes.
